00:58:44,438 --> 00:58:47,601
And this guy is doing
what Norman never did,

768
00:58:47,691 --> 00:58:52,310
which is, you know, "It's your life,
and if you decide to go somewhere else

769
00:58:52,404 --> 00:58:55,942
and whatever you want to do,
