It just creates a lot of tension
because, in a way,

777
00:59:34,946 --> 00:59:38,689
you can't believe that these guys are
just going to let her go just like that.

778
00:59:38,784 --> 00:59:41,321
And there's the door.
Is she going to leave?

779
00:59:42,037 --> 00:59:43,744
Is she going to leave or not?

780
00:59:44,414 --> 00:59:48,282
So I think it works really well.

781
00:59:48,877 --> 00:59:53,917
But then they have
this card up their sleeves.

782
01:00:01,264 --> 01:00:03,471
[woman singing]

783
01:00:09,606 --> 01:00:12,064
This is one of my favorite scenes
