01:00:12,150 --> 01:00:17,486
This reveal that, actually,
Mother was still alive.

785
01:00:17,572 --> 01:00:19,609
[singing]

786
01:00:23,912 --> 01:00:26,950
I love Madelyn's performance here.

787
01:00:27,666 --> 01:00:31,159
Her reaction made it feel
like that song that she sang

788
01:00:31,253 --> 01:00:35,918
in the beginning of the movie is, like,
pushing every cell of her body,

789
01:00:36,007 --> 01:00:37,964
every memory.

790
01:00:39,886 --> 01:00:46,849
It's just tapping into her memories
that were buried

791
01:00:46,935 --> 01:00:48,141
and it's all coming out.

