01:00:48,228 --> 01:00:52,688
And she knows what this means
and she knows what it is.

793
01:00:52,774 --> 01:00:55,641
She's just in deep shock.

794
01:00:59,156 --> 01:01:04,947
This is Fiona O'Shaughnessy,
a wonderful actress from the UK.

795
01:01:06,079 --> 01:01:09,993
And I can't imagine anyone better fit
for this role.

796
01:01:10,083 --> 01:01:11,949
She just killed it.

797
01:01:12,043 --> 01:01:14,910
She got so emotionally invested
in the character.

798
01:01:15,005 --> 01:01:19,044
She just gave an absolutely
astonishing performance, I think.

799
01:01:21,052 --> 01:01:22,759
Like I said...

800
01:01:23,555 --> 01:01:25,296
everything he told you was a lie.

801
01:01:33,440 --> 01:01:35,351
It's a family reunion, finally.

802
01:01:38,361 --> 01:01:41,524
Now we know her actual name, Tara,

803
01:01:41,615 --> 01:01:44,198
and she-- It's new to her.

804
01:01:45,952 --> 01:01:48,694
You... got so big.

805
01:01:52,876 --> 01:01:55,789
[laughs] She looks so creepy.

806
01:02:00,133 --> 01:02:01,373
Come here.

