01:02:01,468 --> 01:02:05,678
And this hug is real, you know?

808
01:02:07,057 --> 01:02:08,889
Phoenix is really feeling it.

809
01:02:08,975 --> 01:02:12,218
It's like this is what she always wanted,
you know, her mom,

810
01:02:12,312 --> 01:02:14,303
and finally she's here. She's alive.

811
01:02:15,357 --> 01:02:17,974
Oh, baby, we missed you so much.

812
01:02:23,114 --> 01:02:26,573
Mmm. There you are.

813
01:02:26,660 --> 01:02:31,871
You were such a beautiful baby.

814
01:02:33,083 --> 01:02:36,576
And this scene is also one of the most
important scenes in the whole movie.

815
01:02:36,670 --> 01:02:40,254
You know,
we're now gonna reveal what the--

816
01:02:40,340 --> 01:02:43,628
What their motivations actually are.

817
01:02:43,718 --> 01:02:45,459
-[Raylan] Get it out. Come on.
-[coughing]

818
01:02:45,553 --> 01:02:48,136
There you go. There you go.

819
01:02:48,223 --> 01:02:49,384
-There you go.
-Sorry.

820
01:02:49,474 --> 01:02:51,010
[Raylan] Nothing to apologize for.

821
01:02:53,228 --> 01:02:54,889
Are you okay?

822
01:02:58,108 --> 01:03:01,521
The same fire that destroyed our family...

823
01:03:01,611 --> 01:03:04,194
I think these two have
a lot of chemistry together.

824
01:03:04,281 --> 01:03:09,947
They make a really creepy
and wonderful couple.

